    "result": {"data":{"cur":{"id":"c07a0c1f-c930-5699-b93a-1e27fb5d626b","html":"<h2 id=\"-배경-관련-속성\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-%EB%B0%B0%EA%B2%BD-%EA%B4%80%EB%A0%A8-%EC%86%8D%EC%84%B1\" aria-label=\" 배경 관련 속성 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>💙 배경 관련 속성</h2>\n<h3 id=\"1-background-color\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-background-color\" aria-label=\"1 background color permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. background-color</h3>\n<p>요소의 <strong>배경 색상</strong><br />\n배경 색상은 배경 이미지보다 뒤에 출력됨</p>\n<ul>\n<li>기본값: transparent - 투명함</li>\n<li>색상: 지정 가능한 색상</li>\n</ul>\n<br />\n<h3 id=\"2-background-image\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-background-image\" aria-label=\"2 background image permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. background-image</h3>\n<p>요소의 <strong>배경 이미지 삽입</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>기본값: none - 이미지 없음</li>\n<li>url(“경로”): 이미지 경로 (따옴표를 붙이는 것이 좋음)</li>\n</ul>\n<br />\n<h3 id=\"3-background-repeat\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-background-repeat\" aria-label=\"3 background repeat permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. background-repeat</h3>\n<p>요소의 <strong>배경 이미지 반복</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>기본값: repeat - 이미지를 수직, 수평 반복</li>\n<li>repeat-x: 이미지를 수평 반복</li>\n<li>repeat-y: 이미지를 수직 반복</li>\n<li>no-repeat: 반복 없음</li>\n</ul>\n<br />\n<h3 id=\"4-background-position\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#4-background-position\" aria-label=\"4 background position permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>4. background-position</h3>\n<p>요소의 <strong>배경 이미지 위치</strong><br />\n보통 방향, 단위로 지정한다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>기본값: 0% 0% - 0% ~ 100% 사이 값</li>\n<li>방향: top, bottom, left, right, center 방향</li>\n<li>단위: px, em, rem 등 단위로 지정</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.item</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> pink<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-image</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token url\"><span class=\"token function\">url</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string url\">'./images/logo.png'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-repeat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> no-repeat<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-position</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> top right<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* 우측 상단에 배치 */</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token property\">background-position</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> center<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* 정 가운데에 배치 */</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token property\">background-position</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100px 30px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* x축 100px, y축 30px 에 배치 */</span></code></pre></div>\n<br />\n<h3 id=\"5-background-size\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#5-background-size\" aria-label=\"5 background size permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>5. background-size</h3>\n<p>요소의 <strong>배경 이미지 크기</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>기본값: auto - 이미지의 <strong>실제 크기</strong></li>\n<li>단위: px, em, rem 등 단위로 지정</li>\n<li>cover: 비율을 유지, 요소의 가로/세로 너비 중 더 <strong>넓은</strong> 너비에 맞춤</li>\n<li>contain: 비율을 유지, 요소의 가로/세로 너비 중 더 <strong>짧은</strong> 너비에 맞춤</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token comment\">/* 가로 150px, 세로 150px */</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">background-size</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 150px 150px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token comment\">/* 가로, 세로 사이즈 중 하나만 명시하면, 자동으로 비율에 맞게 출력됨 */</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">background-size</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<br />\n<h3 id=\"6-background-attachment\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#6-background-attachment\" aria-label=\"6 background attachment permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>6. background-attachment</h3>\n<p>요소의 <strong>배경 이미지 스크롤 특성</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>기본값: scroll - 이미지가 요소를 따라서 같이 스크롤</li>\n<li>fixed: 이미지가 뷰포트에 고정, 스크롤 X (위치가 변경될 때 이미지의 일부만 출력될 수 있음)</li>\n<li>local: 요소 내 스크롤 시 이미지가 같이 스크롤</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">body</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 3000px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">.item</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  ...\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-repeat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> no-repeat<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-position</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> center<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-size</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> cover<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-attachment</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> fixed<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>fixed 로 인해 배경 이미지가 뷰포트에 고정되면서<br />\ncover 는 요소가 아니라, 뷰포트의 더 넓은 너비에 맞춰짐</p>\n<div class=\"table-of-contents\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#-%EB%B0%B0%EA%B2%BD-%EA%B4%80%EB%A0%A8-%EC%86%8D%EC%84%B1\">💙 배경 관련 속성</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#1-background-color\">1. background-color