span>a</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>https://google.com<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Google<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>a</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">a</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> block<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 200px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> orange<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">font-size</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 22px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> white<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">text-decoration</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> none<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* a 태그의 기본 스타일인 밑줄 제거 */</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">text-align</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> center<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* 수평 정렬 */</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">line-height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* 수직 정렬 */</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"1-color\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-color\" aria-label=\"1 color permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. color</h3>\n<p>글자의 <strong>색상</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>기본값: rgb(0, 0, 0) - 검정색</li>\n<li>색상: 기타 지정 가능한 색상</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"2-text-align\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-text-align\" aria-label=\"2 text align permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. text-align</h3>\n<p>문자의 <strong>정렬 방식</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>기본값: left - 왼쪽 정렬</li>\n<li>right: 오른쪽 정렬</li>\n<li>center: 가운데 정렬</li>\n<li>justify: 양쪽 정렬</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"3-text-decoration\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-text-decoration\" aria-label=\"3 text decoration permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. text-decoration</h3>\n<p>문자의 <strong>장식 (선)</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>기본값: none (장식 없음)</li>\n<li>underline: 밑줄</li>\n<li>overline: 윗줄</li>\n<li>line-through: 중앙 선</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"4-text-indent\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#4-text-indent\" aria-label=\"4 text indent permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>4. text-indent</h3>\n<p>문자 첫 줄의 <strong>들여쓰기</strong><br />\n음수 사용 가능 (내어쓰기, outdent)</p>\n<ul>\n<li>기본값: 0 - 들여쓰기 없음</li>\n<li>단위: px, em, rem 등 단위로 지정</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"table-of-contents\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#-%EB%AC%B8%EC%9E%90-%EA%B4%80%EB%A0%A8-%EC%86%8D%EC%84%B1\">💙 문자 관련 속성</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#1-color\">1. color</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#2-text-align\">2. text-align</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#3-text-decoration\">3. text-decoration</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#4-text-indent\">4. text-indent</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>","frontmatter":{"date":"2022.03.13","title":"[CSS] 문자","categories":"CSS","author":"안가을","emoji":null},"fields":{"slug":"/css/character/"}},"prev":{"id":"d7dd8a85-9597-59d0-935c-ce932c213b88","html":"<h2 id=\"-배치-관련-속성\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-%EB%B0%B0%EC%B9%98-%EA%B4%80%EB%A0%A8-%EC%86%8D%EC%84%B1\" aria-label=\" 배치 관련 속성 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>💙 배치 관련 속성</h2>\n<h3 id=\"1-position\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-position\" aria-label=\"1 position permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. position</h3>\n<p>요소의 위치 지정 <strong>기준</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>기본값: static - 기준 없음</li>\n<li>relative: 요소 자신을 기준으로 함</li>\n<li>absolute: 위치 상 부모 요소를 기준으로 함</li>\n<li>fixed: 뷰포트(브라우저)를 기준으로 함</li>\n<li>sticky: 스크롤 영역을 기준으로 함</li>\n</ul>\n<br />\n<h3 id=\"2-position-과-같이-사용하는-css-속성들br-\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-position-%EA%B3%BC-%EA%B0%99%EC%9D%B4-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94-css-%EC%86%8D%EC%84%B1%EB%93%A4br-\" aria-label=\"2 position 과 같이 사용하는 css 속성들br  permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. position 과 같이 사용하는 CSS 속성들<br /></h3>\n<p>모두 음수 사용 가능</p>\n<ul>\n<li>top</li>\n<li>bottom</li>\n<li>left</li>\n<li>right</li>\n<li>z-index</li>\n</ul>\n<br />\n<h3 id=\"3-relative\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-relative\" aria-label=\"3 relative permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. relative</h3>\n<p><strong>요소 자신</strong>을 기준으로 배치한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.child</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> pink<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">position</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> relative<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>relative 라는 특정 기준이 부여되었지만 화면에는 아무런 변화가 없다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.child</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">position</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> relative<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">top</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 30px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">left</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 60px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>자기 자신을 기준으로 위에서 30px, 왼쪽에서 60px 만큼 이동되어 출력된다.<br /></p>\n<p>해당 요소의 기존 위치에는 요소가 차지했던 공간이 그대로 유지되기 때뮨에,<br />\n요소를 원하는 위치에 옮기는 배치의 개념과는 거리가 있다.<br /></p>\n<p>실제로 position: relative 를 사용하는 배치는 거의 사용되지 않는다.</p>\n<br />\n<h3 id=\"4-absolute\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#4-absolute\" aria-label=\"4 absolute permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>4. absolute</h3>\n<p><strong>위치 상 부모 요소</strong>를 기준으로 배치한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>parent<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>child<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>item<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.parent</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 300px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 300px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">bakground-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> red<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">position</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> relative<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* .item 의 구조 상 상위요소 이면서, 위치 상 부모요소임 */</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">.child</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 200px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">bakground-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> orange<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">position</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> static<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* .item 의 구조 상 부모요소 이지만, 위치 상 부모요소가 아님 */</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">.item</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">bakground-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> yellow<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">position</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> absolute<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* 위치 상 부모요소 기준을 찾음 --> .parent */</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">top</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 30px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">left</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 60px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><strong>구조 상 상위 요소들 중에서,</strong><br />\n<strong>position: static 이 아닌 가장 가까운 상위 요소가 위치 상 부모요소</strong>가 된다.<br />\n(대부분의 경우에는 구조 상 부모요소와 위치 상 부모요소가 같다.)</p>\n<p>부모 요소를 기준으로 배치되기 때문에 주변의 다른 요소들과는 상호작용할 필요가 없다.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">absolute</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">fixed</code> 는 기준이 <strong>부모 요소</strong>나 <strong>뷰포트</strong>이기 때문에<br />\n기본적인 레이아웃 구조가 무너진다.</p>\n<p>그렇기 때문에 구조 상의 부모 요소를 <strong>위치 상의 부모 요소</strong>로 만드는<br />\n가장 무난한 값은 <code class=\"language-text\">relative</code> 가 된다.</p>\n<br />\n<h3 id=\"5-fixed\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#5-fixed\" aria-label=\"5 fixed permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>5. fixed</h3>\n<p>뷰포트(브라우저)를 기준으로 배치한다.</p>\n<p>뷰포트를 기준으로 배치되기 때문에 주변의 다른 요소들과는 상호작용할 필요가 없다.<br /></p>\n<p>스크롤을 하더라도 뷰포트 기준으로 <strong>위치가 고정</strong>되기 때뮨에<br />\n주로 <strong>헤더</strong>, <strong>배너</strong> 부분에 사용된다.</p>\n<br />\n<h3 id=\"6-요소-쌓임-순서-stack-order\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#6-%EC%9A%94%EC%86%8C-%EC%8C%93%EC%9E%84-%EC%88%9C%EC%84%9C-stack-order\" aria-label=\"6 요소 쌓임 순서 stack order permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>6. 요소 쌓임 순서 (Stack order)</h3>\n<p>어떤 요소가 <strong>사용자와 더 가깝게 있는지 (위에 쌓이는지)</strong> 결정</p>\n<ol>\n<li>요소에 <code class=\"language-text\">position</code> 속성의 <strong>값이 있는 경우</strong> 위에 쌓인다. (static 제외)</li>\n<li>1번 조건이 같은 경우, <code class=\"language-text\">z-index</code> 속성의 숫자 <strong>값이 높을 수록</strong> 위에 쌓인다.</li>\n<li>1번과 2번 조건이 같은 경우, <code class=\"language-text\">HTML</code>의 <strong>다음 구조</strong>일 수록 위에 쌓인다. (더 나중에 작성된 것)</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>parent<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>child<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>child<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>child<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token comment\">/* 1번째 */</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">.parent .child:nth-child(1)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">position</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> relative<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">z-index</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* 2번째 */</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">.parent .child:nth-child(2)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">position</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> absolute<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* 3번째 */</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">.parent .child:nth-child(3)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">position</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> fixed<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">z-index</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>요소 쌓임 순서: 2번째 - 1번째 - 3번째</p>\n<br />\n<h3 id=\"7-z-index\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#7-z-index\" aria-label=\"7 z index permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>7. z-index</h3>\n<p>요소의 쌓임 정도를 지정</p>\n<ul>\n<li>기본값: auto (0) - 부모 요소와 동일한 쌓임 정도</li>\n<li>숫자: 숫자가 높을 수록 위에 쌓임</li>\n</ul>\n<p>z-index 값으로는 되도록 큰 숫자를 사용하지 않는 것이 좋다.<br />\n나중에 다른 요소를 해당 요소보다 위에 쌓기 위해서 z-index 의 값이 계속해서 커지고,<br />\n그렇게 되면 코드가 복잡해지고 관리가 어려워 지기 때문이다.</p>\n<br />\n<h3 id=\"8-요소의-display-가-변경됨\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#8-%EC%9A%94%EC%86%8C%EC%9D%98-display-%EA%B0%80-%EB%B3%80%EA%B2%BD%EB%90%A8\" aria-label=\"8 요소의 display 가 변경됨 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>8. 요소의 display 가 변경됨</h3>\n<p>position 속성의 값으로 <code class=\"language-text\">absolute</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">fixed</code> 가 지정된 요소는,<br />\n<strong>display 속성이 block</strong> 으로 변경된다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.text1</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> block<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">position</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> absolute<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">top</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 30px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">left</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 30px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">z-index</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">.text2</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">position</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> absolute<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">top</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 30px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">left</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 30px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">z-index</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>위의 두 요소는 같은 스타일을 가진다.<br />\n.text2 에는 자동으로 display: block; 스타일이 적용된다.</p>\n<div class=\"table-of-contents\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#-%EB%B0%B0%EC%B9%98-%EA%B4%80%EB%A0%A8-%EC%86%8D%EC%84%B1\">💙 배치 관련 속성</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#1-position\">1. position</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#2-position-%EA%B3%BC-%EA%B0%99%EC%9D%B4-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94-css-%EC%86%8D%EC%84%B1%EB%93%A4br-\">2. position 과 같이 사용하는 CSS 속성들<br /></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#3-relative\">3. relative</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#4-absolute\">4. absolute</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#5-fixed\">5. fixed</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#6-%EC%9A%94%EC%86%8C-%EC%8C%93%EC%9E%84-%EC%88%9C%EC%84%9C-stack-order\">6. 요소 쌓임 순서 (Stack order)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#7-z-index\">7. z-index</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#8-%EC%9A%94%EC%86%8C%EC%9D%98-display-%EA%B0%80-%EB%B3%80%EA%B2%BD%EB%90%A8\">8. 요소의 display 가 변경됨</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>","frontmatter":{"date":"2022.03.13","title":"[CSS] 배치","categories":"CSS","author":"안가을","emoji":null},"fields":{"slug":"/css/positioning/"}},"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"https://autumnly1007.github.io","comments":{"utterances":{"repo":"autumnly1007/autumnly1007.github.io"}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/css/background/","nextSlug":"/css/character/","prevSlug":"/css/positioning/"}},
    "staticQueryHashes": ["1073350324","1956554647","2938748437"]}